  m_RaycastPadding: {x: 0, y: 0, z: 0, w: 0}
  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_FontData:
    m_Font: {fileID: 10102, guid: 0000000000000000e000000000000000, type: 0}
    m_FontSize: 20
    m_FontStyle: 0
    m_BestFit: 0
    m_MinSize: 0
    m_MaxSize: 40
    m_Alignment: 4
    m_AlignByGeometry: 0
    m_RichText: 1
    m_HorizontalOverflow: 0
    m_VerticalOverflow: 0
    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: "ABOUT\n\nThe SILK team has travelled over 6000 km, visiting over 30 caravanserais,
    in west \rand central Turkey, to carefully and meticulously recreate these beautiful
    sites. We \rhave created a digital virtual reality experience of each, for all
    to enjoy. Our goal is \rto preserve, protect and remember this important part
    of Turkish heritage.\r\n\nPARTNERS AND SPONSORS\n\nThe SILK project directed
    by Assoc. Prof. G\xFCzden Varinlio\u011Flu, in the field of digital heritage,
    is \rfunded by the U.S. Department of State, in partnership with Assoc. Prof.
    Takehiko Nagakura, of \rthe Design Computation Lab, Department of Architecture
    at Massachusetts Institute of \rTechnology (MIT)\n"
